\par\plain {\f3\fs24\b1\i1 \line }{\f4\fs24\b0\i0 Forty years ago, I was born in the royal pond of the Westminster palace.  I was the crown princess of the Goldfish family, meaning I would inherit everything. Where humans had always seen men as the most important sex, we Goldfish see females as the stronger sex. }}